        "subject": "LU-9184 mdc: move layout data to the lr_lvb_data",
        "message": "LU-9184 mdc: move layout data to the lr_lvb_data\n\nLayout data is stored in lock lvb on client side and it\nmakes impossible to use this LVB for Data-on-MDT IO lock\nat the same time. Patch moves this data to the resource lvb\nwhich is not used on client, leaving lock lvb data for DoM\npurposes. This is for testing purposes for now.\n\nSigned-off-by: Mikhal Pershin <mike.pershin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I1e93fad07e154324f7ebb48b0690cd4a23b84efb\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
